3336	  Let \(f : Y \to X\) be a morphism of schemes. On the monoidal unit pair
3337	  \((\mathcal{O}_X, \mathcal{O}_X)\) the sheaf-level comparison
3338	  \[
3339	    \delta_{(\mathcal{O},\mathcal{O})} :
3340	      f^*(\mathcal{O}_X \otimes_X \mathcal{O}_X)
3341	      \;\longrightarrow\;
3342	      f^*\mathcal{O}_X \otimes_Y f^*\mathcal{O}_X
3343	  \]
