3376	  \cref{lem:isiso_sheafifyeta_of_unitsquare} yields
3377	  \(\mathtt{IsIso}\bigl(a_Y.\mathrm{map}\,(\eta\,(\mathtt{pullback}\,\varphi'))\bigr)\) --- the
3378	  right-hand side \(\mathtt{pullbackObjUnitToUnit}\,\varphi = \mathtt{pullbackUnitIso}\,f :
