3424	  \(\mathtt{Adjunction.unit\_app\_unit\_comp\_map\_}\eta\) instantiated at the presheaf
3425	  pullback--pushforward adjunction \(\mathtt{pullbackPushforwardAdjunction}\,\varphi'\). That
3426	  identity holds for any adjunction whose left adjoint is oplax monoidal and whose right adjoint
3427	  is lax monoidal in a mate-compatible way. The compatible pair is
3428	  \(\mathtt{presheafPushforwardLaxMonoidal}\)
3429	  (\cref{lem:presheaf_pushforward_laxmonoidal}) and \(\mathtt{presheafPullbackOplaxMonoidal}\)
3430	  (\cref{lem:presheaf_pullback_oplaxmonoidal}), so the
3431	  mate identity applies to the concrete adjunction and yields the stated equation.
